						               													<description>DESCRIPTION:&amp;#10;Have you ever wanted to rule the world?  Now you can do so -- with Global Control!  This is a card game where 2-6 players compete by using power cards and strategy to outsmart and outplay fellow players.  Your objective is to take control of countries from around the globe.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Do you save your powerful cards to capture a key country?  Do you sabotage your friends?  Do you sit back and watch two competitors duke it out and waste their resources?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With eighty different countries and ninety-six power cards, anything is possible.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAME OBJECTIVE:&amp;#10;Have the most points once 20 random countries are owned.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAMEPLAY:&amp;#10;Players take turns bidding on countries, using 'power cards'.  The highest bidder takes control of the country which moves them closer to global domination.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAME ELEMENTS:&amp;#10;&amp;bull;Players can collect cards and store up additional firepower to control key countries&amp;#10;&amp;bull;Many cards affect the effectiveness of other cards, creating player contention&amp;#10;&amp;bull;Countries provide additional 'special powers' that can be leveraged&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
